title: Ted Gushue
description:
Ted Gushue is a photographer, writer, and digital media consultant. Previously the Executive Editor of Petrolicious, you might follow his current work on @type7, a Porsche-sponsored Instagram account that's more daily digital magazine than just photos of cars.

Follow Type 7 on IG @type7

Check him out at @tedgushue.

Follow us!

T: @thesmokingtire @zackklapman

IG: @thesmokingtire @fakezackklapman

 

Watch the show on  YouTube: https://youtu.be/fYt3jDz8IRQ
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
